-- Aegis Plans to Make Acquisitions, Sees Advertising Growth, Horizont Says
-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 2012-01-05T11:22:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/aegis-plans-to-make-acquisitions-sees-ad-growth-horizont-says.html
Aegis Group Plc (AGS)  is looking for
acquisitions in social media, mobile marketing and technology,
the German weekly media newsletter  Horizont  reported today,
citing Chief Executive Officer Jerry Buhlmann.  The advertising strategy company will focus its attention
on growth regions such as  Brazil , Russia, India and China,
Horizont said, citing Buhlmann.  The global advertising market will grow 6 percent this year
while the European market will remain “relatively stable,” the
executive said, according to Horizont.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ragnhild Kjetland in Frankfurt at 
